{"tid":2019841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"當局至今就梨木樹邨感染群組收回的檢測樣本全呈陰性","createTime":"2020-05-16T14:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T16:13:06.000Z","uid":166360,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7476bad80b352c0b7cae262b7548318fa6ad11c9","tid":2019841,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:32:32.000Z","msg":"當局至今就梨木樹邨感染群組收回的檢測樣本全呈陰性<br />\n2020-05-16 HKT 22:30<br />\n<br />\n衞生署表示，截至今日上午9時，就荃灣梨木樹邨感染群組，共派出2104個深喉唾液樣本瓶，收回及檢測106個樣本，全部對新型冠狀病毒測試呈陰性反應。<br />\n<br />\n衛生防護中心早前表示，仍在調查梨木樹邨感染群組個案的源頭，相關的梨木樹邨居民及部分街市檔販、卓明樓居民、補習社相關人士，以及男患者所經營鐘錶維修檔的顧客，都會被安排檢測。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526604-20200516.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526604-20200516.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=9ae0d498\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526604-20200516.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=55c5f7d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526604-20200516.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"469555c9a70c83cc41908343dbab267d6cfda17b","tid":2019841,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:34:06.000Z","msg":"即係仲有2000個未驗?"},{"pid":"692c2b08cb77544a2468477b0f236845ed3ee4b1","tid":2019841,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"469555c9a70c83cc41908343dbab267d6cfda17b","tid":2019841,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:34:06.000Z","msg":"即係仲有2000個未驗?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T15:17:49.000Z","msg":"照原文理解應該是有2000個未收到"},{"pid":"ed6cfbf4c565159d6eeb918fea58109f2eca1c0a","tid":2019841,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T15:20:19.000Z","msg":"驗荃灣街市會唔會比較可能有陽性"},{"pid":"61a3a304c9da8753dd54b4bf3ce05e76